<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>超智引擎 - 智能生成专业项目分析</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='style_new.css') }}">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="app-header" id="appHeader">
        <div class="header-container">
            <div class="header-content">
                <button id="backToHomeBtn" class="back-btn" style="display: none;" aria-label="返回首页">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <div class="header-logo">
                    <div class="logo-icon">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                            <path d="M9.5 2A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 12 4.5v15a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-4.96.44L2 22M14 2a2.5 2.5 0 0 0-2.5 2.5v15a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 4.96.44L22 22"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="logo-text">
                        <h1>超智引擎</h1>
                        <p>智能生成专业项目分析</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="header-actions">
                    <a href="/admin" class="admin-link" style="margin-left: 10px; color: #667eea; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 8px; transition: all 0.2s; font-weight: 500;">管理</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <!-- 验证码输入模态框 -->
    <div class="modal-overlay" id="verifyCodeModal" style="display: none;">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h2>输入验证码</h2>
                <button class="modal-close" onclick="hideVerifyCodeModal()">&times;</button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p class="modal-description">请输入您的验证码以获得使用次数</p>
                <input type="text" id="verifyCodeInput" class="verify-code-input" placeholder="XXXXXX-XXXXXX-XXXXXX-XXXXXX" maxlength="27">
                <div class="modal-error" id="verifyCodeError" style="display: none;"></div>
                <button class="modal-submit-btn" onclick="submitVerifyCode()">验证</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="app-main" id="appMain">
        <!-- Hero Section (Home) -->
        <section class="hero-section" id="heroSection">
            <div class="hero-container">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <div class="hero-badge">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>AI 驱动的智能分析</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h2 class="hero-title">专业的项目可行性报告</h2>
                    
                    <p class="hero-description">
                        基于人工智能技术，为您的项目提供全方位的可行性分析，包括市场评估、财务分析、风险评估和专业建议
                    </p>
                    
                    <button id="startProjectBtn" class="hero-cta-btn">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
                        </svg>
                        开始创建报告
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div class="features-grid">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon feature-icon-blue">
                            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                                <polyline points="23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18"/>
                                <polyline points="17 6 23 6 23 12"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3>智能市场分析</h3>
                        <p>AI 分析行业趋势和市场机会，为您提供数据驱动的洞察</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon feature-icon-purple">
                            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                                <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3>全面风险评估</h3>
                        <p>识别潜在风险点，提供专业的风险应对策略和建议</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon feature-icon-indigo">
                            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                                <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3>快速生成报告</h3>
                        <p>几分钟内获得专业完整的可行性报告，节省时间成本</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="process-card">
                    <h3 class="process-title">报告生成流程</h3>
                    <div class="process-steps">
                        <div class="process-step">
                            <div class="step-number">1</div>
                            <h4>填写项目信息</h4>
                            <p>提供基本的项目详情</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="process-step">
                            <div class="step-number">2</div>
                            <h4>AI 智能分析</h4>
                            <p>系统自动进行深度分析</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="process-step">
                            <div class="step-number">3</div>
                            <h4>生成专业报告</h4>
                            <p>获得完整可行性报告</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="process-step">
                            <div class="step-number">4</div>
                            <h4>导出与分享</h4>
                            <p>下载或分享给团队</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Project Form Section -->
        <section class="form-section" id="formSection" style="display: none;">
            <div class="form-container">
                <div class="form-card">
                    <div class="form-header">
                        <h2>项目信息填写</h2>
                        <p>请详细填写项目信息，以便 AI 为您生成更准确的可行性报告</p>
                    </div>

                    <form id="projectForm" class="project-form">
                        <div class="form-grid">
                            <div class="form-field">
                                <label>项目名称 <span class="required">*</span></label>
                                <input type="text" id="projectName" name="projectName" placeholder="例如：智慧城市管理平台" required>
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-field">
                                <label>建设单位 <span class="required">*</span></label>
                                <input type="text" id="constructionUnit" name="constructionUnit" placeholder="例如：XX科技有限公司" required>
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-field">
                                <label>项目类型 <span class="required">*</span></label>
                                <select id="projectType" name="projectType" required>
                                    <option value="">请选择</option>
                                    <option value="新建项目">新建项目</option>
                                    <option value="扩建项目">扩建项目</option>
                                    <option value="改建项目">改建项目</option>
                                    <option value="迁建项目">迁建项目</option>
                                    <option value="恢复项目">恢复项目</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-field">
                                <label>所属行业 <span class="required">*</span></label>
                                <select id="industry" name="industry" required>
                                    <option value="">请选择</option>
                                    <option value="互联网/科技">互联网/科技</option>
                                    <option value="金融服务">金融服务</option>
                                    <option value="教育">教育</option>
                                    <option value="医疗健康">医疗健康</option>
                                    <option value="制造业">制造业</option>
                                    <option value="零售/电商">零售/电商</option>
                                    <option value="房地产">房地产</option>
                                    <option value="能源环保">能源环保</option>
                                    <option value="其他">其他</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-field">
                                <label>预计预算 <span class="required">*</span></label>
                                <select id="budget" name="budget" required>
                                    <option value="">请选择</option>
                                    <option value="10万以下">10万以下</option>
                                    <option value="10-50万">10-50万</option>
                                    <option value="50-100万">50-100万</option>
                                    <option value="100-500万">100-500万</option>
                                    <option value="500-1000万">500-1000万</option>
                                    <option value="1000万以上">1000万以上</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-field">
                                <label>项目周期 <span class="required">*</span></label>
                                <select id="timeline" name="timeline" required>
                                    <option value="">请选择</option>
                                    <option value="3个月以内">3个月以内</option>
                                    <option value="3-6个月">3-6个月</option>
                                    <option value="6-12个月">6-12个月</option>
                                    <option value="1-2年">1-2年</option>
                                    <option value="2年以上">2年以上</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-field">
                                <label>团队规模 <span class="required">*</span></label>
                                <select id="teamSize" name="teamSize" required>
                                    <option value="">请选择</option>
                                    <option value="1-5人">1-5人</option>
                                    <option value="6-10人">6-10人</option>
                                    <option value="11-20人">11-20人</option>
                                    <option value="21-50人">21-50人</option>
                                    <option value="50人以上">50人以上</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-field form-field-full">
                            <label>目标市场 <span class="required">*</span></label>
                            <input type="text" id="targetMarket" name="targetMarket" placeholder="例如：一线城市的中小企业、年轻消费群体等" required>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-field form-field-full">
                            <label>项目描述 <span class="required">*</span></label>
                            <textarea id="description" name="description" rows="4" placeholder="请详细描述您的项目内容、目标、核心价值等..." required></textarea>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-field form-field-full">
                            <label>附件上传 <span class="optional">(可选)</span></label>
                            <p class="field-hint">上传项目相关文档，如商业计划书、市场调研报告、财务预测等</p>
                            <div class="file-upload-area" id="fileUploadArea">
                                <input type="file" id="fileUpload" multiple accept=".pdf,.doc,.docx,.xls,.xlsx,.ppt,.pptx,.txt" style="display: none;">
                                <label for="fileUpload" class="file-upload-label">
                                    <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                                        <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/>
                                        <polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"/>
                                        <line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="15"/>
                                    </svg>
                                    <span>点击上传文件或拖拽到这里</span>
                                    <span class="file-upload-hint">支持 PDF, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, TXT 格式</span>
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <div id="uploadedFilesList" class="uploaded-files-list"></div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- 兑换码输入区域 -->
                        <div class="form-field form-field-full" style="margin-top: 32px; padding-top: 24px; border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb; background: #f9fafb; padding: 24px; border-radius: 12px;">
                            <label style="display: block; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; color: #1f2937; margin-bottom: 8px;">
                                兑换码 <span class="optional" style="color: #6b7280; font-weight: normal;">(可选)</span>
                            </label>
                            <p class="field-hint" style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">
                                输入兑换码可获得使用次数，每次使用会消耗1次使用次数
                            </p>
                            <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start;">
                                <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 0;">
                                    <input 
                                        type="text" 
                                        id="redeemCodeInput" 
                                        class="redeem-code-input" 
                                        placeholder="XXXXXX-XXXXXX-XXXXXX-XXXXXX" 
                                        maxlength="27" 
                                        style="width: 100%; padding: 14px 16px; border: 2px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; transition: all 0.3s; background: white; box-sizing: border-box;"
                                        onfocus="this.style.borderColor='#667eea'; this.style.boxShadow='0 0 0 3px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1)';"
                                        onblur="this.style.borderColor='#d1d5db'; this.style.boxShadow='none';"
                                    >
                                    <div class="redeem-error" id="redeemCodeError" style="display: none; color: #dc3545; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 8px; padding-left: 4px;"></div>
                                </div>
                                <button 
                                    type="button" 
                                    id="redeemCodeBtn" 
                                    class="redeem-btn" 
                                    onclick="redeemCode()" 
                                    style="padding: 14px 32px; background: #667eea; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; white-space: nowrap; box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2); height: fit-content;"
                                    onmouseover="if(!this.disabled) { this.style.background='#5568d3'; this.style.transform='translateY(-1px)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 8px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3)'; }"
                                    onmouseout="if(!this.disabled) { this.style.background='#667eea'; this.style.transform='translateY(0)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 2px 4px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2)'; }"
                                >
                                    <span id="redeemBtnText">兑换</span>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-actions">
                            <button type="submit" id="submitFormBtn" class="submit-btn" disabled>
                                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="spinner" style="display: none;">
                                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke-opacity="0.25"/>
                                    <path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 1 10 10" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                                </svg>
                                <span id="submitBtnText">生成可行性报告</span>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Report Display Section -->
        <section class="report-section" id="reportSection" style="display: none;">
            <div class="report-container" id="reportContainer">
                <!-- Report will be rendered here by JavaScript -->
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- PDF生成库 -->
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/html2pdf.js/0.10.1/html2pdf.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='report-display.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='app_new.js') }}"></script>
</body>
</html>

